</taxonomicName>
(incorrect subsequent spelling): Farzanpay, 1988: 41; Kovařík, 1993: 203; Fet &amp; Lowe, 2000: 222.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BC736BDFFD9FFB597A6F883FD0FF8B7" blockId="2.[192,803,1754,1899]" box="[192,666,1876,1899]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1">
